                    <span>2017-05-12</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">虽然观点和角度有亮点，但整体枯燥，可读性差。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1176758652">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1176758652" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1176758652" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1176758652">有用</a>
